-- Comdaq Metals Appoints Blundell to Head Singapore Iron-Ore Unit
-- B y   G l e n y s   S i m
-- 2012-03-25T16:00:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-25/comdaq-metals-appoints-blundell-to-head-singapore-iron-ore-unit.html
Comdaq Metals Ltd., an over-the-
counter broker and online trading platform for precious metals,
appointed Oliver Blundell to head its new iron-ore business in
 Singapore , the London-based company said.  Blundell has more than 24 years of bulk commodities and
shipping experience gained with Cargill Inc., Comdaq said in a
statement today. More recently, he was head of front office at
iron-ore pricing platform globalORE, Blundell said.  “We want to provide a platform for all physical iron-ore
products for smaller miners who struggle to find a
marketplace,” Blundell said in an interview in Singapore on
March 23.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Glenys Sim in Singapore at 
